Dialogue: 1,0:01:09.71,0:01:11.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,多美好的一天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.71,0:01:11.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What a wonderful day
Dialogue: 1,0:01:12.21,0:01:15.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,阳光明媚  波光粼粼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.21,0:01:15.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The sun is out, the water is shimmering
Dialogue: 1,0:01:15.05,0:01:16.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,贝壳快乐地叫着
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.05,0:01:16.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,scallops are chirping
Dialogue: 1,0:01:17.59,0:01:19.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好安静
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.59,0:01:19.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So peaceful
Dialogue: 1,0:01:27.35,0:01:29.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拜托能不能小点声
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.35,0:01:29.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can we lower the volume, please
Dialogue: 1,0:01:29.90,0:01:32.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这么吵害我干不了正事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.90,0:01:32.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't work with all that racket going on
Dialogue: 1,0:01:32.98,0:01:34.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好的  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.98,0:01:34.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sure thing, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:01:34.99,0:01:35.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这才对
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.99,0:01:35.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Right
Dialogue: 1,0:01:36.65,0:01:37.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.65,0:01:37.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 1,0:01:53.80,0:01:57.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在来听听章鱼哥竖笛的美妙音乐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.80,0:01:56.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And now for some soothing sounds
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.05,0:01:57.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,from Squidward's clarinet
Dialogue: 1,0:01:58.34,0:01:59.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢  谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.34,0:01:59.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you, thank you
Dialogue: 1,0:02:12.65,0:02:13.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.65,0:02:13.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I thought I--
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.40,0:02:18.24,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(835,180)}泡泡
Dialogue: 1,0:02:15.65,0:02:18.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  要不要来吹泡泡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.65,0:02:18.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Squidward, want to blow some bubbles?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:18.24,0:02:19.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只要两毛五
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.24,0:02:19.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Only 25 cents
Dialogue: 1,0:02:20.20,0:02:20.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太对了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.20,0:02:20.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Right
Dialogue: 1,0:02:20.95,0:02:25.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,搞得好像我会浪费时间吹泡泡一样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.95,0:02:25.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,like I would spend a moment of my time blowing bubbles
Dialogue: 1,0:02:26.70,0:02:28.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,行行好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.70,0:02:28.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, please
Dialogue: 1,0:02:28.16,0:02:31.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是说  谁会特别花钱去吹泡泡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.16,0:02:31.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I mean, who in the world would pay to blow bubbles?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:32.71,0:02:34.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.71,0:02:34.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good morning
Dialogue: 1,0:02:38.05,0:02:39.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.05,0:02:39.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, boy
Dialogue: 1,0:02:39.05,0:02:40.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你也早  先生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.05,0:02:40.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good morning to you, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:02:40.64,0:02:41.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要来吹泡泡吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.64,0:02:41.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Would you care to blow a bubble?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:43.30,0:02:44.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要多少钱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.30,0:02:44.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How much is it?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:44.93,0:02:46.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只要两毛五
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.93,0:02:46.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Only a quarter
Dialogue: 1,0:02:46.47,0:02:48.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,价格挺合理
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.47,0:02:48.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sounds reasonable
Dialogue: 1,0:02:50.60,0:02:52.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我得去借两毛五
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.60,0:02:52.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm going to need to borrow a quarter
Dialogue: 1,0:02:53.11,0:02:53.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没问题  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.11,0:02:53.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sure thing, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:02:55.78,0:02:57.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,两毛五
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.78,0:02:57.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,One quarter
Dialogue: 1,0:03:01.53,0:03:02.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.53,0:03:02.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you
Dialogue: 1,0:03:03.12,0:03:05.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,生意火起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.12,0:03:05.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Business is booming
Dialogue: 1,0:03:08.66,0:03:12.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我怎么会跟这么废的邻居住在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.66,0:03:12.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How did I ever get surrounded by such loser neighbors?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.71,0:03:18.67,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(987,324)}泡泡
Dialogue: 1,0:03:17.42,0:03:18.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一根泡泡棒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.42,0:03:18.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,One bubble wand
Dialogue: 1,0:03:18.92,0:03:20.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蘸完泡泡水可以吹了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.92,0:03:20.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,dipped and ready to go
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.46,0:03:52.00,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(417,898)}教程
Dialogue: 1,0:03:57.04,0:03:58.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,愿意参与教程吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.04,0:03:58.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Could I interest you in some lessons?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:58.67,0:03:59.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只要两毛五
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.67,0:03:59.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Only 25 cents
Dialogue: 1,0:04:01.72,0:04:03.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.72,0:04:03.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Very well, then
Dialogue: 1,0:04:04.39,0:04:06.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  我能再借两毛五吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.39,0:04:06.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, sponge, can I borrow another quarter?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:08.68,0:04:09.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.68,0:04:09.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks
Dialogue: 1,0:04:10.02,0:04:11.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  全都在于技巧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.02,0:04:11.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, Patrick, it's all in the technique
Dialogue: 1,0:04:12.06,0:04:13.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,首先这样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.06,0:04:13.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,First go like this
Dialogue: 1,0:04:13.81,0:04:14.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,转个圈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.81,0:04:14.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,spin around
Dialogue: 1,0:04:14.73,0:04:15.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,停
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.73,0:04:15.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,stop
Dialogue: 1,0:04:15.73,0:04:17.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,甩头回神三遍
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.73,0:04:17.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Double-take three times
Dialogue: 1,0:04:17.44,0:04:19.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一  二  三
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.44,0:04:19.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,one, two, three
Dialogue: 1,0:04:19.73,0:04:21.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然后骨盆俯冲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.73,0:04:21.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,then pelvic thrust
Dialogue: 1,0:04:25.24,0:04:26.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,用右脚站住
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.24,0:04:26.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stop on your right foot
Dialogue: 1,0:04:26.49,0:04:27.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,记住这一点
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.49,0:04:27.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't forget it
Dialogue: 1,0:04:27.83,0:04:31.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在开始转个大圈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.83,0:04:31.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now it's time to bring it around town
Dialogue: 1,0:04:31.41,0:04:34.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,转个大圈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.41,0:04:34.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bring it around town
Dialogue: 1,0:04:34.42,0:04:36.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然后你这样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.42,0:04:36.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Then you do this
Dialogue: 1,0:04:36.25,0:04:37.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再这样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.25,0:04:37.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,then this
Dialogue: 1,0:04:37.25,0:04:37.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.25,0:04:37.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and this
Dialogue: 1,0:04:37.96,0:04:38.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然后那样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.96,0:04:38.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,then that
Dialogue: 1,0:04:38.50,0:04:39.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这样那样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.50,0:04:39.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and this and that
Dialogue: 1,0:04:39.84,0:04:40.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然后
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.84,0:04:40.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and then--
Dialogue: 1,0:05:23.80,0:05:26.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在用两只手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.80,0:05:26.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And now with two hands
Dialogue: 1,0:05:34.35,0:05:35.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是头长颈鹿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.35,0:05:35.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's a giraffe
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.38,0:06:05.26,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(891,802)}打烊
Dialogue: 1,0:06:06.17,0:06:07.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好意思先生  我们打烊了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.17,0:06:07.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, sir, but we are close
Dialogue: 1,0:06:07.59,0:06:09.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别说有的没的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.59,0:06:09.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't give me any of that
Dialogue: 1,0:06:09.59,0:06:10.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们两个吹个泡泡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.59,0:06:10.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How could you two possibly make
Dialogue: 1,0:06:10.93,0:06:13.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么会那么吵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.93,0:06:13.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,all this noise just blowing bubbles?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.06,0:06:16.68,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(745,268)}泡泡
Dialogue: 1,0:06:13.06,0:06:14.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们不仅仅是在吹泡泡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.06,0:06:14.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're not just blowing bubbles
Dialogue: 1,0:06:14.97,0:06:16.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们是在创造泡泡艺术
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.97,0:06:16.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,we're making bubble art
Dialogue: 1,0:06:17.23,0:06:18.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.23,0:06:18.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Watch carefully
Dialogue: 1,0:06:18.48,0:06:20.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,首先这样
