Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.73,0:18:52.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What do you need?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:54.86,0:18:57.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,裁缝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.86,0:18:57.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A tailor
Dialogue: 1,0:18:58.32,0:19:00.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因为我撕破了我的裤子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.32,0:19:00.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Because I ripped my pants
Dialogue: 1,0:19:03.12,0:19:05.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这种玩笑开得一点不是时候
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.12,0:19:05.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That kind of stuff is uncalled for
Dialogue: 1,0:19:05.41,0:19:06.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么鬼玩意
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.41,0:19:06.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What is that?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:08.96,0:19:10.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一点都不好笑  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.96,0:19:10.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That wasn't funny, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:19:10.75,0:19:12.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你害我担心死了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.75,0:19:12.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Y'all had me worried sick
Dialogue: 1,0:19:16.92,0:19:18.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老兄
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.92,0:19:18.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Dude
Dialogue: 1,0:19:23.43,0:19:24.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快啊  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.43,0:19:24.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:19:24.76,0:19:25.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要失去他们了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.76,0:19:25.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you're losing them
Dialogue: 1,0:19:25.56,0:19:26.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快想
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.56,0:19:26.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Think
Dialogue: 1,0:19:26.14,0:19:27.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你观众还在等着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.14,0:19:27.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your public's waiting
Dialogue: 1,0:19:28.68,0:19:29.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我想想
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.68,0:19:29.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's see
Dialogue: 1,0:19:30.02,0:19:31.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,举重  大笑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.02,0:19:31.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Lifting weights, big laugh
Dialogue: 1,0:19:31.90,0:19:33.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,飞盘砸中脸  笑翻
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.90,0:19:33.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Frisbee in face, kills
Dialogue: 1,0:19:33.69,0:19:35.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,冲浪  笑死
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.69,0:19:35.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Surfing, knocks them dead
Dialogue: 1,0:19:36.02,0:19:37.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,假装溺水
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.02,0:19:37.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pretending to drown
Dialogue: 1,0:19:38.32,0:19:39.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.32,0:19:39.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,no
Dialogue: 1,0:19:40.24,0:19:41.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快想啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.24,0:19:41.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, think
Dialogue: 1,0:19:42.86,0:19:43.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.86,0:19:43.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got it
Dialogue: 1,0:19:44.99,0:19:46.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.99,0:19:46.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, everybody
Dialogue: 1,0:19:46.62,0:19:48.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没有破裤子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.62,0:19:48.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not ripped pants
Dialogue: 1,0:19:49.54,0:19:51.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,裤子已经被扒下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.54,0:19:51.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,pants ripped off
Dialogue: 1,0:19:52.08,0:19:53.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有谁来报个警
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.08,0:19:53.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Someone call the police
Dialogue: 1,0:19:53.67,0:19:55.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有个在逃裤子贼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.67,0:19:55.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's a pants thief on the loose
Dialogue: 1,0:20:04.14,0:20:04.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.14,0:20:04.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no
Dialogue: 1,0:20:05.39,0:20:08.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家都走了  连珊迪也是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.39,0:20:08.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Everybody's gone, even Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:20:08.01,0:20:10.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,她宁愿跟拉里在一块
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.01,0:20:10.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,She'd rather hang out with Larry
Dialogue: 1,0:20:10.39,0:20:10.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.39,0:20:10.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no
Dialogue: 1,0:20:11.60,0:20:14.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.60,0:20:14.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:20:14.98,0:20:16.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们搞砸了  裤子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.98,0:20:16.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We blew it, pants
Dialogue: 1,0:20:18.15,0:20:19.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁跟你算是  我们
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.15,0:20:19.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who do you mean, we?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:23.11,0:20:24.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我根本没必要卖傻
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.11,0:20:24.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I didn't have to be a fool
Dialogue: 1,0:20:24.45,0:20:25.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来引起珊迪的注意
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.45,0:20:25.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to get Sandy's attention
Dialogue: 1,0:20:26.24,0:20:29.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是海滩最大的失败者吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.24,0:20:29.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Am I the biggest loser on the beach?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:29.49,0:20:31.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不  我才是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.49,0:20:31.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, I am
Dialogue: 1,0:20:31.25,0:20:33.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我忘记涂防晒霜了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.25,0:20:33.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I forgot to put on sunscreen
Dialogue: 1,0:20:37.42,0:20:38.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不  我才是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.42,0:20:38.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, I am
Dialogue: 1,0:20:38.96,0:20:41.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我面包上沾上了沙子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.96,0:20:41.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got sand in my buns
Dialogue: 1,0:20:46.39,0:20:49.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不  我才是海滩最大的失败者
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.39,0:20:49.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, I'm the biggest loser on the beach
Dialogue: 1,0:20:50.06,0:20:52.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们把我埋进沙子里  还把我忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.06,0:20:52.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They buried me in the sand and forgot me
Dialogue: 1,0:20:53.39,0:20:55.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.39,0:20:55.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What happened to you?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:55.85,0:20:57.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我失去了我的好朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.85,0:20:57.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I lost my best friend
Dialogue: 1,0:20:58.40,0:20:59.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.40,0:20:59.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:02.11,0:21:03.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,当我撕裂了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.11,0:21:03.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,When I ripped
Dialogue: 1,0:21:04.57,0:21:05.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的裤子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.57,0:21:05.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My pants
Dialogue: 1,0:21:06.70,0:21:10.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我以为所有人都会喜欢我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.70,0:21:10.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I thought that I had everybody on my side
Dialogue: 1,0:21:10.41,0:21:14.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但我搞砸了一切
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.41,0:21:14.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But I went and blew it all sky-high
Dialogue: 1,0:21:14.46,0:21:18.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在她连看都不会看我一眼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.46,0:21:18.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And now she won't even spare a passing glance
Dialogue: 1,0:21:18.54,0:21:20.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全都是因为我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.54,0:21:20.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All just because I
Dialogue: 1,0:21:21.30,0:21:22.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,弄破裤子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.30,0:21:22.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ripped my pants
Dialogue: 1,0:21:22.59,0:21:26.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拉里过来  让海绵宝宝显得渺小
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.59,0:21:26.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,When big Larry came round just to put him down
Dialogue: 1,0:21:26.30,0:21:30.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,于是海绵宝宝成了小丑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.30,0:21:30.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob turned into a clown
Dialogue: 1,0:21:30.31,0:21:33.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,女生们都不愿共舞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.31,0:21:33.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And no girl ever wants to dance
Dialogue: 1,0:21:33.98,0:21:38.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,同一个破裤子的傻瓜一起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.98,0:21:38.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,With a fool who went and ripped his pants
Dialogue: 1,0:21:38.06,0:21:40.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我知道不该闷闷不乐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.06,0:21:40.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know I shouldn't mope around
Dialogue: 1,0:21:40.19,0:21:41.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也不该埋怨
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.19,0:21:41.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I shouldn't curse
Dialogue: 1,0:21:41.98,0:21:44.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但我心中的痛愈发严重
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.98,0:21:44.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But the pain feels so much worse
Dialogue: 1,0:21:45.78,0:21:49.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因为没人理  让一切变乏味
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.78,0:21:49.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,'Cause winding up with no one is a lot less fun
Dialogue: 1,0:21:49.41,0:21:51.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,程度大于晒伤
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.41,0:21:51.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Than a burn from the sun
Dialogue: 1,0:21:51.58,0:21:54.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有面包沾沙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.58,0:21:54.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Or sand in your buns
Dialogue: 1,0:21:57.92,0:22:01.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在我学到了难忘的教训
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.92,0:22:01.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now I learned a lesson I won't soon forget
Dialogue: 1,0:22:01.21,0:22:05.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在听好  不然就会后悔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.21,0:22:05.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So listen and you won't regret
Dialogue: 1,0:22:05.13,0:22:07.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对自己真诚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.13,0:22:07.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Be true to yourself
Dialogue: 1,0:22:07.22,0:22:09.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要错过机会
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.22,0:22:09.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't miss your chance
Dialogue: 1,0:22:09.18,0:22:11.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你就不会变成
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.18,0:22:11.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And you won't end up
Dialogue: 1,0:22:11.14,0:22:17.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,破裤子的那个傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.14,0:22:17.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Like the fool who ripped his pants
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.78,0:22:29.11,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1045,310)}海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 1,0:22:29.53,0:22:30.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.53,0:22:30.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:22:31.07,0:22:31.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.07,0:22:31.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:22:35.70,0:22:37.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你的歌唱得太对了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.70,0:22:37.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your song is true
Dialogue: 1,0:22:37.50,0:22:40.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要想成为朋友  就只要做好自己
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.50,0:22:40.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If y'all want to be my friend just be yourself
Dialogue: 1,0:22:40.67,0:22:43.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  说得太对了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.67,0:22:43.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, that was so righteous
Dialogue: 1,0:22:43.59,0:22:46.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你愿意在我裤子上签名吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.59,0:22:46.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Would you sign my pants?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:46.21,0:22:47.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以  兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.21,0:22:47.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Absolutely, buddy
